  "wechat_html": "<img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzXgUR7FJnf11qGIo8nmKt6RxibXrb5s4RFb9UZ9UOHQy7fqQyI377Licw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'><section style='padding:0;'><section style=\"margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f6efe4 0%,#fbf8f2 58%,#ffffff 100%);padding:1px;color:#1f2937;\"><section style=\"width:100%;margin:0;\"><section style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.16);box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:relative;background:#d6d3d1;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-14/hf-event-00.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block;\"></div><section style=\"padding:16px 12px 10px;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:#111827;color:#f9fafb;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">History Today</div><h1 style=\"font-size:29px;line-height:1.22;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#111827;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;\">历史上的今天：伊夫里战役的胜利</h1><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#475569;margin:0;\">回顾1590年法国伊夫里战役，亨利四世率军取得关键性胜利。</p></section><section style=\"padding:0 10px 12px;\"><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">在1590年的今天，法国历史上发生了一场影响深远的军事冲突——伊夫里战役。当时，亨利四世率领胡格诺派军队，与天主教联盟的军队展开了激烈的较量。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-14/hf-event-01.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">这场战役是法国宗教战争期间的关键时刻。亨利四世展现了卓越的指挥才能，成功击败了由马耶纳公爵查理统帅的联盟军队，为后续的局势发展奠定了基础。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-14/hf-event-02.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">除了这场著名的战役，历史上的3月14日也见证了其他权力的更迭。例如在1489年的这一天，威尼斯共和国逼迫塞浦路斯王国女王卡特琳娜·科纳罗退位，并正式取得了该岛的行政管理权。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-14/hf-event-03.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">时间回溯到更早的1074年，匈牙利也曾发生过重大的王权之争。在莫焦罗德战役中，盖萨公爵和拉斯洛公爵联手击败了当时的国王所罗门，迫使其撤离。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-14/hf-event-04.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">历史长河中，这些事件记录了不同时代权力的博弈与军事的兴衰。无论是战场上的胜负，还是政治上的退位，都深刻地塑造了当时欧洲乃至地中海区域的政治版图。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-14/hf-event-05.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div></section></section></section></section></section><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzk57DCmhVC16o9ILH0Tn1YPEiarfLRRQSVFN2mJdeYibGnBPialPIzvojw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'>"
